text: Hi. I am trying to understand how chaincode is executed on Hyperledger.  Whenever I deploy a Java or Go smart contract, where is it registered/stored inside Hyperledger?   Also, when I invoke a smart contract does it run inside a Docker protected image?
hi <@U17CZFXGU>, since you talk about Go I assume you're actually referring to Hyperledger Fabric
you will have better chance getting your questions specific to Fabric answered on <#C0Y4PEU22|fabric>
this channel is for the Architecture WG which works on a higher level than any of the several Hyperledger frameworks under development (fabric, sawtooth lake, iroha)
